    Exception Description
    FieldNotValidException

    InvalidClientIdInOrder

    InvalidJsonException
    If Json is invalid, this exception will be thrown.
    OrderAlreadyExistingException
    This exception represents if an order already exists.
    OrderNotFoundException
    Exception if the order is not found.
    OrderStatusCannotBeChangedException
    If an order status cannot be changed.
    UserAlreadyExistingException
    If an user already exists in the system.
    UserNotAuthorizedException
    If user is not authorized to perform an action.
    UserNotFoundException
    If User is not found in the system.
